snippet: Alexis Sanchez has said he is very happy at Arsenal but the Chile winger has put the onus on the north London club to put an end to the protracted contract negotiations to keep him at the Emirates Stadium....
lead_paragraph: Alexis Sanchez has said he is very happy at Arsenal but the Chile winger has put the onus on the north London club to put an end to the protracted contract negotiations to keep him at the Emirates Stadium.

headline.main: Sanchez Puts Onus on Arsenal to End Contract Stand-Off
headline.print_headline: Sanchez Puts Onus on Arsenal to End Contract Stand-Off
